00:23:06.610 --> 00:23:11.570 align:middle line:84%
"Who are we, if not measured
by our impact on others?

00:23:11.570 --> 00:23:13.295 align:middle line:90%
That's who we are.

00:23:13.295 --> 00:23:15.470 align:middle line:90%
We are not who we say we are.

00:23:15.470 --> 00:23:17.840 align:middle line:90%
We're not who we want to be.

00:23:17.840 --> 00:23:22.130 align:middle line:84%
We are sum of the influence
and impact that we have

00:23:22.130 --> 00:23:27.310 align:middle line:90%
in our lives and on others."

00:23:27.310 --> 00:23:32.980 align:middle line:84%
Walk soft, live light,
let go, but hold tight.

00:23:32.980 --> 00:23:35.410 align:middle line:84%
This is truly a long
roller coaster of soul

00:23:35.410 --> 00:23:39.880 align:middle line:84%
that we are all on until
the clock ticks last for us.

00:23:39.880 --> 00:23:43.000 align:middle line:84%
And I hope you find what you're
looking for before that time.

